@node "intro"

@{u}Introduction@{uu}

This is version V1.5 of SolarProbe. created in Blitz Basic 2.1.

SolarProbe shows the positions of the planets from Mercury to Saturn, as seen
at any date from space or from Earth!


SolarProbe V1.5 includes the following features:

* Fast operation, even on a 68020.
* Two viewmodes:- from space, or Earth.
* Dynamic viewpoints- zoom, rotate, incline.
* Shows useful, up-to-date information about each planet.
* Ideal for beginners, No understanding of astronomy required.


@endnode
